---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import NavSimple from '../components/NavSimple.astro';
import '../styles/submit.css';

const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<Layout
  title="投稿・信息纠错 | 81日本"
  description="向 81日本 提交新医院信息、纠正现有错误，或提供其他建议，共同完善在日中文医疗信息库。"
  path="/submit"
  noindex={true}
  locale="zh"
>
  <NavSimple locale="zh" />

  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">投稿</div>
    <h1>帮我<em>完善</em>这份指南</h1>
    <p>知道某家提供中文服务的医院还没收录？或者发现信息有误？都欢迎告诉我。</p>
  </div>

  <div class="page-main">
    <aside class="side-info">
      <h3>投稿流程</h3>
      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">1</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">填写表单</div>
            <div class="step-desc">告诉我医院名称、地址及语言服务等信息</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">2</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">人工核实</div>
            <div class="step-desc">收到通知后我会核实信息的准确性</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-num">3</div>
          <div class="step-body">
            <div class="step-title">更新上线</div>
            <div class="step-desc">确认无误后更新到网站，通常 1–3 天内完成</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="side-note">纠错请注明具体问题及信息来源，这样能更快处理。</div>
    </aside>

    <div>
      <div class="form-card" id="formCard">
        <div class="type-row">
          <button class="type-btn active" onclick="switchType('new', this)">＋ 新增医院</button>
          <button class="type-btn" onclick="switchType('fix', this)">✎ 纠错/补充</button>
          <button class="type-btn" onclick="switchType('other', this)">⊙ 其他建议</button>
        </div>

        <form class="form" id="submitForm" action="/api/submit" method="POST">
          <input type="hidden" name="投稿类型" id="typeHidden" value="新增医院" />
          <input type="text" name="_honey" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" aria-hidden="true" style="position:absolute; left:-9999px; opacity:0" />

          <div id="fields-new">
            <div class="form-row">
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label">医院名称 <span class="req">*</span></label>
                <input class="form-input" type="text" name="医院名称" id="f-name" placeholder="中文或日文均可" />
              </div>
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label">所在地 <span class="req">*</span></label>
                <input class="form-input" type="text" name="所在地" id="f-location" placeholder="都道府县・城市" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row" style="margin-top:0">
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label">语言服务 <span class="req">*</span></label>
                <select class="form-input form-select" name="语言服务" id="f-lang">
                  <option value="">请选择…</option>
                  <option value="中文（普通话）">中文（普通话）</option>
                  <option value="中文（广东话）">中文（广东话）</option>
                  <option value="中文＋英文">中文＋英文</option>
                  <option value="英文">英文</option>
                  <option value="其他">其他</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label">科室</label>
                <input class="form-input" type="text" name="科室" placeholder="内科、産科、歯科…" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row" style="margin-top:0">
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label">电话号码</label>
                <input class="form-input" type="text" name="电话" placeholder="03-XXXX-XXXX" />
              </div>
              <div class="form-field">
                <label class="form-label">官网 / SNS</label>
                <input class="form-input" type="text" name="网址" placeholder="https://…" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label class="form-label">营业时间</label>
              <input class="form-input" type="text" name="营业时间"
                placeholder="例：周一至周五 9:00–17:30 / 周六 9:00–12:30" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label class="form-label">备注</label>
              <textarea class="form-input form-textarea" name="备注" id="f-note"
                placeholder="是否需要预约、休息日、注意事项等…"
                oninput="updateChar(this,'c1')"></textarea>
              <div class="char-count" id="c1">0 / 300</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div id="fields-fix" style="display:none">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label class="form-label">哪家医院 <span class="req">*</span></label>
              <input class="form-input" type="text" name="纠错-医院名称" id="f-fix-name" placeholder="医院名称" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label class="form-label">问题描述 <span class="req">*</span></label>
              <textarea class="form-input form-textarea" name="纠错-问题描述" id="f-fix-desc"
                placeholder="哪里有误？正确信息是什么？如有来源请附上。"
                style="min-height:110px" oninput="updateChar(this,'c2')"></textarea>
              <div class="char-count" id="c2">0 / 300</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div id="fields-other" style="display:none">
            <div class="form-field">
              <label class="form-label">你的建议 <span class="req">*</span></label>
              <textarea class="form-input form-textarea" name="建议内容" id="f-other"
                placeholder="功能建议、内容补充等…"
                style="min-height:110px" oninput="updateChar(this,'c3')"></textarea>
              <div class="char-count" id="c3">0 / 300</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="form-divider"></div>

          <div class="form-field">
            <label class="form-label">联系方式（选填）</label>
            <input class="form-input" type="text" name="联系方式" placeholder="邮箱、微信、LINE ID 均可" />
          </div>

          <button class="submit-btn" type="submit" id="submitBtn">
            <span id="btnText">提交投稿</span>
          </button>
          <p class="form-note">提交即表示你同意我将信息用于网站内容更新</p>
        </form>
      </div>

      <div class="success-card" id="successCard">
        <div class="success-icon">✓</div>
        <h3>已收到，谢谢！</h3>
        <p>我会尽快核实并更新。<br>如果你留了联系方式，有疑问时我会回复你。</p>
        <div class="success-actions">
          <button class="success-btn success-btn-primary" onclick="resetForm()">再提交一条</button>
          <a href="/" class="success-btn success-btn-secondary">返回首页</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <div>© {year} 81日本 · 由 81Japan 维护</div>
    <a href="/" style="color:var(--ink-3); text-decoration:none; font-size:12px;">← 返回首页</a>
  </footer>

  <script is:inline src="/submit.js" defer></script>
</Layout>
